#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.166"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.166:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.166:0.2"
msgid "16. Nandikkhayavagga"
msgstr "16. The End of Relishing"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 166. Sakkāyadiṭṭhipahānasutta → sakkāyadiṭṭhippahānasuttaṃ (bj) | sakkāya (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.166:0.3"
msgid "166. Sakkāyadiṭṭhipahānasutta"
msgstr "166. Giving Up Identity View"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.166:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu … pe …"
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn35.166:1.2"
msgid "etadavoca:"
msgstr "and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn35.166:1.3"
msgid ""
"“kathaṃ nu kho, bhante, jānato kathaṃ passato sakkāyadiṭṭhi pahīyatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Sir, how does one know and see so that identity view is given up?”"

msgctxt "sn35.166:1.4"
msgid "“Cakkhuṃ kho, bhikkhu, dukkhato jānato passato sakkāyadiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicant, knowing and seeing the eye, sights, eye consciousness, and eye "
"contact as suffering, identity view is given up. …"

msgctxt "sn35.166:1.5"
msgid "Rūpe dukkhato jānato passato sakkāyadiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.166:1.6"
msgid "Cakkhuviññāṇaṃ dukkhato jānato passato sakkāyadiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.166:1.7"
msgid "Cakkhusamphassaṃ dukkhato jānato passato sakkāyadiṭṭhi pahīyati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.166:1.8"
msgid ""
"yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā "
"adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi dukkhato jānato passato sakkāyadiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""
"And also knowing and seeing the pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that "
"arises conditioned by mind contact as suffering, identity view is given up."

msgctxt "sn35.166:1.9"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhu, jānato evaṃ passato sakkāyadiṭṭhi pahīyatī”ti."
msgstr "This is how to know and see so that identity view is given up.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.166:1.10"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
